{"metadata":{"title":"OUDSCheckbox","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckbox"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents12OUDSCheckboxV","roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckbox","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","text":"Indicator states","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This checkbox indicator has two available states:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to use a tri-state checkbox instead, refer to ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","text":"Particular cases","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text